      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a project or a source of parts. The exterior has extensive rust along the rocker panels and wheel arches, and there is a noticeable crack in the windshield. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with several tears and deep stains, and the air conditioning is currently non-functional. Mechanically, the engine runs but has a persistent oil leak and requires immediate attention to the suspension system. It is being sold strictly as-is.",
