    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offering a museum-quality 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Carbon Black. This S54-powered icon features a high-revving 3.2L straight-six with individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. Comprehensive mechanical provenance includes a full VANOS overhaul, VAC coated rod bearing replacement, and a reinforced rear subframe with TMS plates. The chassis dynamics are preserved via a factory-spec refreshed suspension and a perfectly functioning variable M differential lock. Zero oil pan seepage, no subframe fatigue, and factory-spec compression across all six cylinders. This is an investment-grade enthusiast's vehicle with all critical preventative maintenance performed to the highest standard.",
